            <lg xml:id="TK77">
<l>eṉpi lataṉai veyilpōlak kāyumē</l>
<l>yaṉpi lataṉai yaṟam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just as sunheat burns the boneless creature, so</l>
<l>does dharma burn the loveless one.</l>
            </lg>
